      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PRINCESS TILLEY (2) has an excellent record over this course and distance having never missed the placings in eight starts, including five wins and three placings. Comes off a (19.70) win last time, scoring by a nose in a Grade 3/4 over 342m at Angle Park. Makes strong appeal on best. IMAGINE THE FUN (7) placed last time (19.57) at Murray Bridge Straight in a Grade 4/5, finishing second and beaten half a length. Has two wins already from this draw. Looks well placed here and among the chances. CARRY ON CASEY (4) missed the hat-trick last start when second and beaten a neck (19.50) last time at Angle Park. Solid record at the distance winning six races. Ran one of the fastest times on the program last start despite finishing in the minors. Expected to feature again. PARABOLE RICO (8) placed last time (22.49) at Murray Bridge in a Grade 3/4/5, finishing third and beaten 6 lengths. Already a winner from this draw.",
